  ($vsq$八、電源電路迴路辨識（Flyback）$vsq$, $vsq$下圖為返馳式 (Flyback) 充電器電路。請標出：(1) 一次側<strong>主迴路</strong>線段（開關切換的大電流路徑）；(2) 一次側<strong>高壓線段</strong>（提示：會與部分主迴路線段重疊）。展開看電路圖與解答。$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">F1</text><line x1="80" y1="55" x2="100" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="24" y1="87" x2="100" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="100" y="42" width="50" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="125" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L1</text><text x="125" y="92" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CM</text><line x1="150" y1="55" x2="170" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="150" y1="87" x2="170" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="170" y="42" width="60" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="200" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">BD1</text><line x1="230" y1="70" x2="420" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="280" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="340" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="305" y="62" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">HV+</text><line x1="240" y1="98" x2="240" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="60" y1="310" x2="455" y2="310" st