"/><line x1="477" y1="90" x2="477" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="70" x2="540" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><polygon points="540,63 540,77 552,70" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="552" y1="63" x2="552" y2="77" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="546" y="59" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">D3</text><line x1="552" y1="70" x2="700" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="620" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="600" y1="70" x2="600" y2="156" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="156" x2="600" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="172" x2="611" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="180" x2="611" y2="180" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="180" x2="600" y2="196" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="616" y="180" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace">Cout</text><line x1="600" y1="196" x2="600" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="688" y="58" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT+</text><text x="688" y="296" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT-</text><line x1="700" y1="70" x2="700" y2="76" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="700" y1="310" x2="700" y2="304" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="170" x2="477" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="477" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="620" y1="70" x2="620" y2="340" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="585" y="340" width="70" height="34" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="620" y="361" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">TL431</text><line x1="585" y1="352" x2="510" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="450" y="334" width="60" height="40" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="480" y="358" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">U2</text><text x="480" y="384" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">OPTO</text><line x1="450" y1="352" x2="210" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="352" x2="210" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="249" x2="240" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="310" x2="430" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="352" x2="424" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="424" y1="344" x2="424" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="344" x2="416" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="352" x2="380" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="380" y1="352" x2="380" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="380" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="420" y="336" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CY</text><line x1="477" y1="20" x2="477" y2="60" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><line x1="477" y1="300" x2="477" y2="326" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><text x="477" y="14" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">ISOLATION</text><path d="M280,70 H432 V310 H280 Z" fill="none" stroke="#eab308" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M88,55 H170 M88,87 H170" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M230,70 H432 V236" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:12px;margin:4px 0"><span style="display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;background:#eab308;margin:0 4px 0 10px"></span>黃＝主迴路（大電流）<span style="display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;background:#ef4444;margin:0 4px 0 10px"></span>紅＝高壓線段</div><strong>主迴路（黃）：</strong>大電容 C1 → 變壓器一次繞組 → Q1 → 感流電阻 Rs → 回 C1。Q1 導通期間的開關大電流走這一圈，di/dt 最大——佈局面積必須最小，C1 要緊貼變壓器與 Q1。<br><strong>高壓線段（紅）：</strong>保險絲之後的 AC 線、整流橋、直流母線 HV+（90–264VAC 整流後約 120–370VDC）、一次繞組到 Q1 汲極——關斷時汲極再疊加反射電壓與漏感尖波，可達 600V 級。<br><strong>為什麼重疊：</strong>主迴路本身就跑在高壓母線上——C1→一次繞組→汲極這段既是大電流路徑也是高壓節點，佈局要同時顧 EMI（迴路最小）與安規（爬電/間隙）。<div class="key-point">面試官考的是「會不會跟著電流走一圈」：先找大電容（迴路源頭），沿開關元件繞一圈＝主迴路；從整流橋輸出沿母線到開關節點＝高壓段。</div>$vsq$, $vsq$The figure shows a flyback charger. Mark (1) the primary-side <strong>main loop</strong> (the high-current switching path) and (2) the primary-side <strong>high-voltage segments</strong> (hint: they overlap part of the main loop). Expand for the schematic and answer.$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">F1</text><line x1="80" y1="55" x2="100" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="24" y1="87" x2="100" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="100" y="42" width="50" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="125" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L1</text><text x="125" y="92" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" te