I 全部惡化。Cout 的 ESL 也算在迴路裡，所以 Cout 要緊貼 D3 與繞組接腳，必要時多顆 MLCC 並聯就近放。<div class="key-point">Flyback 佈局三大迴路：一次熱迴路（C1-P-Q1-Rs）、二次整流迴路（S-D3-Cout）、閘極驅動迴路——面試答得出三個就贏一半。</div>$vsq$, $vsq$On the same flyback, mark the <strong>secondary-side main loop</strong> (the output-rectification high-current path) and explain why its area must be as small as possible.$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">F1</text><line x1="80" y1="55" x2="100" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="24" y1="87" x2="100" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="100" y="42" width="50" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="125" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L1</text><text x="125" y="92" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CM</text><line x1="150" y1="55" x2="170" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="150" y1="87" x2="170" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="170" y="42" width="60" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="200" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">BD1</text><line x1="230" y1="70" x2="420" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="280" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="340" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="305" y="62" fill="#00d4ff" font-siz