x1="416" y1="352" x2="380" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="380" y1="352" x2="380" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="380" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="420" y="336" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CY</text><line x1="477" y1="20" x2="477" y2="60" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><line x1="477" y1="300" x2="477" y2="326" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><text x="477" y="14" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">ISOLATION</text><path d="M477,70 H600 V310 H477 V90" fill="none" stroke="#eab308" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:12px;margin:4px 0"><span style="display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;background:#eab308;margin:0 4px 0 10px"></span>노랑=주 루프(대전류)</div><strong>2차측 주 루프(노랑):</strong> 2차 권선 → 출력 정류 D3 → 출력 커패시터 Cout → 권선으로 복귀.<br><strong>면적 최소화 이유:</strong> 플라이백 2차 전류는 Q1 오프 기간에만 흐르는 <strong>펄스형 대전류</strong>로 di/dt가 매우 큼; 루프 면적이 크면 기생 인덕턴스가 커져 → D3 턴오프 링잉, 전압 오버슈트, 방사 EMI 모두 악화. Cout의 ESL도 루프의 일부이므로 Cout을 D3와 권선 핀에 밀착시키고 필요 시 MLCC 병렬로 근접 배치.<div class="key-point">플라이백 레이아웃 3대 루프: 1차 핫 루프(C1-P-Q1-Rs), 2차 정류 루프(S-D3-Cout), 게이트 구동 루프——셋 다 말하면 면접 절반은 이긴 것.</div>$vsq$),
  ($vsq$八、電源電路迴路辨識（Flyback）$vsq$, $vsq$開關雜訊會經變壓器一二次繞組間的寄生電容跑到二次側，形成共模 EMI。請標出這條<strong>共模雜訊路徑</strong>，並說明 Y 電容 (CY) 的作用與擺放原則。$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">F1</text><line x1="80" y1="55" x2="100" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="24" y1="87" x2="100" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="100" y="42" width="50" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="125" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L1</text><text x="125" y="92" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CM</text><line x1="150" y1="55" x2="170" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="150" y1="87" x2="170" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="170" y="42" width="60" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="200" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">BD1</text><line x1="230" y1="70" x2="420" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="280" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="340" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="305" y="62" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">HV+</text><line x1="240" y1="98" x2="240" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="60" y1="310" x2="455" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><t