bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="450" y="334" width="60" height="40" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="480" y="358" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">U2</text><text x="480" y="384" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">OPTO</text><line x1="450" y1="352" x2="210" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="352" x2="210" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="249" x2="240" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="310" x2="430" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="352" x2="424" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="424" y1="344" x2="424" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="344" x2="416" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="352" x2="380" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="380" y1="352" x2="380" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="380" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="420" y="336" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CY</text><line x1="477" y1="20" x2="477" y2="60" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><line x1="477" y1="300" x2="477" y2="326" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><text x="477" y="14" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">ISOLATION</text><path d="M432,214 L448,130 L462,130 L477,150 V310 M477,310 H430 V352 H380 V310 M380,310 H432" fill="none" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:12px;margin:4px 0"><span style="display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;background:#22c55e;margin:0 4px 0 10px"></span>綠＝訊號/雜訊路徑</div><strong>共模路徑（綠）：</strong>雜訊源＝Q1 汲極（SW 節點）的高 dv/dt → 經一二次繞組間寄生電容 Cps 打到二次側 → 沿二次地流動 → 經 <strong>CY 回到一次地</strong>，短路回雜訊源。<br><strong>沒有 CY 會怎樣：</strong>雜訊電流只能經輸出線、人體/大地、LISN 繞一大圈回來＝共模傳導 EMI 直接超標。<br><strong>CY 擺放：</strong>跨接一次地–二次地（或一次 HV+–二次地），選安規 Y1/Y2 電容；容值受漏電流限制（一般 ≤4.7nF，貼牆式常 1~2.2nF）；位置緊靠變壓器、兩端走線最短，讓雜訊迴圈最小。<div class="key-point">共模 EMI 的思路是「幫雜訊找一條最短的回家路」——Y 電容就是那條路。</div>$vsq$, $vsq$Switching noise couples to the secondary through the transformer interwinding capacitance, creating common-mode EMI. Mark this <strong>common-mode noise path</strong> and explain the role and placement of the Y-capacitor (CY).$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">F1</text><line x1="80" y1="55" x2="100" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="24" y1="87" x2="100" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="100" y="42" width="50" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="125" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L1</text><text x="125" y="92" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CM</text><line x1="150" y1="55" x2="170" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="150" y1="87" x2="170" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="170" y="42" width="60" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="200" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">BD1</text><line x1="230" y1="70" x2="420" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stro