0" y1="258" x2="330" y2="258" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="425" y="258" width="14" height="34" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="447" y="278" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="9" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace">Rs</text><line x1="432" y1="292" x2="432" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="90" x2="477" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="70" x2="540" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><polygon points="540,63 540,77 552,70" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="552" y1="63" x2="552" y2="77" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="546" y="59" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">D3</text><line x1="552" y1="70" x2="700" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="620" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="600" y1="70" x2="600" y2="156" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="156" x2="600" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="172" x2="611" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="180" x2="611" y2="180" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="180" x2="600" y2="196" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="616" y="180" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace">Cout</text><line x1="600" y1="196" x2="600" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="688" y="58" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT+</text><text x="688" y="296" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT-</text><line x1="700" y1="70" x2="700" y2="76" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="700" y1="310" x2="700" y2="304" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="170" x2="477" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="477" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="620" y1="70" x2="620" y2="340" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="585" y="340" width="70" height="34" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="620" y="361" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">TL431</text><line x1="585" y1="352" x2="510" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="450" y="334" width="60" height="40" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="480" y="358" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">U2</text><text x="480" y="384" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">OPTO</text><line x1="450" y1="352" x2="210" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="352" x2="210" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="249" x2="240" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="310" x2="430" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="352" x2="424" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="424" y1="344" x2="424" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="344" x2="416" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="352" x2="380" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="380" y1="352" x2="380" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="380" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="420" y="336" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CY</text><line x1="477" y1="20" x2="477" y2="60" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><line x1="477" y1="300" x2="477" y2="326" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><text x="477" y="14" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">ISOLATION</text><path d="M432,214 L448,130 L462,130 L477,150 V310 M477,310 H430 V352 H380 V310 M380,310 H432" fill="none" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:12px;margin:4px 0"><span style="display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;background:#22c55e;margin:0 4px 0 10px"></span>Green = signal/noise path</div><strong>Common-mode path (green):</strong> the noise source is the high dv/dt at the Q1 drain (SW node) → through the interwinding capacitance Cps to the secondary → along the secondary ground → back to primary ground <strong>through CY</strong>, shorting back to the source.<br><strong>Without CY:</strong> the noise current can only return through the output cable, body/earth and the LISN in a huge loop = conducted common-mode EMI fails outright.<br><strong>CY placement:</strong> bridge primary ground to secondary ground (or primary HV+ to secondary ground) with a safety-rated Y1/Y2 cap; value is limited by leakage current (usually ≤4.7nF, wall adapters often 1-2.2nF); place it tight to the transformer with the shortest possible leads so the noise loop is minimal.<div class="key-point">Common-mode EMI thinking = give the noise the shortest way home - the Y-cap is that way.</div>$vsq$, $vsq$8. Power-Circuit Loop Identification (Flyback)$vsq$, $vsq$八、電源回路のループ識別（フライバック）$vsq$, $vsq$8. 전원 회로 루프 식별(플라이백)$vsq$, $vsq$スイッチングノイズはトランスの一二次巻線間寄生容量を通って二次側へ流れ、コモンモード EMI になります。この<strong>コモンモードノイズ経路</strong>を示し、Y コンデンサ (CY) の役割と配置原則を説明してください。$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" te