——走線遠離變壓器、Q1 汲極、RCD 箝位；分壓中點（TL431 REF 腳）最敏感，分壓電阻靠 TL431 放、走線最短；光耦兩側各自屬於一次地與二次地，不可為了省事跨區亂繞。<div class="key-point">輸出無故振盪/抖動時，先查 FB 走線是不是貼著 SW 節點跑——這是返馳最常見的佈局翻車點。</div>$vsq$, $vsq$Mark the <strong>feedback signal path</strong> from the output voltage to the controller FB pin (through the TL431 and the optocoupler), and explain what feedback routing must stay away from.$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">F1</text><line x1="80" y1="55" x2="100" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="24" y1="87" x2="100" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="100" y="42" width="50" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="125" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L1</text><text x="125" y="92" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CM</text><line x1="150" y1="55" x2="170" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="150" y1="87" x2="170" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="170" y="42" width="60" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="200" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">BD1</text><line x1="230" y1="70" x2="420" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="280" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="340" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="305" y="62" 