動路徑（橘，上）：</strong>HV+ 母線 → 啟動電阻 Rst → VDD（對 VDD 電容充電到 UVLO 開啟門檻，IC 開始切換）。<br><strong>正常供電（橘，下）：</strong>切換建立後，輔助繞組 AUX → D2 整流 → VDD 接手供電；AUX 電壓與輸出成匝比比例，一次側調節 (PSR) 架構還兼做輸出電壓感測。<br><strong>待機功耗：</strong>Rst 掛在高壓母線上，P≈V²/R 全時存在——365VDC 下 1MΩ 也吃 0.13W，直接吃掉 <30mW 級待機規格。對策：加大阻值（犧牲啟動時間）、多顆分壓（耐壓）、或選有 HV 啟動腳（內建 JFET 電流源，啟動後關斷）的控制 IC。<div class="key-point">VDD 電容要撐過「啟動到 AUX 接手」的空窗——太小會打嗝式重啟（hiccup），面試常拿這個追問。</div>$vsq$, $vsq$At power-up the auxiliary winding has no voltage yet. Mark the controller <strong>start-up supply path</strong> and the <strong>auxiliary supply path</strong> in normal operation, and explain how the start-up resistor relates to standby power.$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">N</text><line x1="24" y1="55" x2="46" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="46" y="49" width="34" height="12" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="63" y="45" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">F1</text><line x1="80" y1="55" x2="100" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="24" y1="87" x2="100" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="100" y="42" width="50" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="125" y="74" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L1</text><text x="125" y="92" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CM</text><line x1="150" y1="55" x2="170" y2="55" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="150" y1="87" x2="170" y2="87" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="170" y="42" width="60" height="56" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x