432" y1="246" x2="350" y2="246" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="350" y1="246" x2="350" y2="258" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="350" y1="258" x2="330" y2="258" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="425" y="258" width="14" height="34" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="447" y="278" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="9" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace">Rs</text><line x1="432" y1="292" x2="432" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="90" x2="477" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="70" x2="540" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><polygon points="540,63 540,77 552,70" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="552" y1="63" x2="552" y2="77" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="546" y="59" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">D3</text><line x1="552" y1="70" x2="700" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="620" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="600" y1="70" x2="600" y2="156" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="156" x2="600" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="172" x2="611" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="180" x2="611" y2="180" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="180" x2="600" y2="196" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="616" y="180" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace">Cout</text><line x1="600" y1="196" x2="600" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="688" y="58" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT+</text><text x="688" y="296" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT-</text><line x1="700" y1="70" x2="700" y2="76" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="700" y1="310" x2="700" y2="304" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="170" x2="477" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="477" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="620" y1="70" x2="620" y2="340" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="585" y="340" width="70" height="34" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="620" y="361" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">TL431</text><line x1="585" y1="352" x2="510" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="450" y="334" width="60" height="40" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="480" y="358" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">U2</text><text x="480" y="384" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">OPTO</text><line x1="450" y1="352" x2="210" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="352" x2="210" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="249" x2="240" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="310" x2="430" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="352" x2="424" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="424" y1="344" x2="424" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="344" x2="416" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="352" x2="380" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="380" y1="352" x2="380" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="380" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="420" y="336" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CY</text><line x1="477" y1="20" x2="477" y2="60" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><line x1="477" y1="300" x2="477" y2="326" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><text x="477" y="14" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">ISOLATION</text><path d="M340,70 V185 H255 V200" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M397,255 V210 M397,197 V185 H360" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:12px;margin:4px 0"><span style="display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;background:#f97316;margin:0 4px 0 10px"></span>Orange = supply path</div><strong>Start-up path (orange, top):</strong> HV+ bus → start-up resistor Rst → VDD (charges the VDD cap to the UVLO turn-on threshold, then the IC starts switching).<br><strong>Normal supply (orange, bottom):</strong> once switching is established, AUX winding → D2 rectifier → VDD takes over; the AUX voltage tracks the output by turns ratio, and primary-side-regulation (PSR) designs also use it for output-voltage sensing.<br><strong>Standby power:</strong> Rst hangs on the HV bus so P≈V²/R burns continuously - even 1MΩ at 365VDC eats 0.13W, wrecking a <30mW standby budget. Fixes: larger resistance (slower start-up), several resistors in series (voltage rating), or a controller with an HV start-up pin (internal JFET current source that shuts off after start).<div class="key-point">The VDD cap must bridge the gap from start-up until AUX takes over - too small and the supply hiccups. A favorite interview follow-up.</div>$vsq$, $vsq$8. Power-Circuit Loop Identification (Flyback)$vsq$, $vsq$八、電源回路のループ識別（フライバック）$vsq$, $vsq$8. 전원 회로 루프 식별(플라이백)$vsq$, $vsq$電源投入直後は補助巻線にまだ電圧がありません。IC の<strong>起動給電経路</strong>と通常動作時の<strong>補助給電経路</strong>を示し、起動抵抗と待機電力の関係を説明してください。$vsq$, $vsq$<div class="exam-diagram-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 720 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="720" height="400" fill="#0a0a1a"/><text x="16" y="59" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">L</text><text x="16" y="91" fill="#00d4ff" font-s