 stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="90" x2="477" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="70" x2="540" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><polygon points="540,63 540,77 552,70" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="552" y1="63" x2="552" y2="77" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="546" y="59" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">D3</text><line x1="552" y1="70" x2="700" y2="70" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><circle cx="620" cy="70" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="600" y1="70" x2="600" y2="156" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="156" x2="600" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="172" x2="611" y2="172" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="589" y1="180" x2="611" y2="180" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="600" y1="180" x2="600" y2="196" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="616" y="180" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="10" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace">Cout</text><line x1="600" y1="196" x2="600" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="600" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="688" y="58" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT+</text><text x="688" y="296" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">VOUT-</text><line x1="700" y1="70" x2="700" y2="76" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="700" y1="310" x2="700" y2="304" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="477" y1="170" x2="477" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="477" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><line x1="620" y1="70" x2="620" y2="340" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="585" y="340" width="70" height="34" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="620" y="361" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">TL431</text><line x1="585" y1="352" x2="510" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="450" y="334" width="60" height="40" fill="none" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="480" y="358" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">U2</text><text x="480" y="384" fill="#c8d4ee" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">OPTO</text><line x1="450" y1="352" x2="210" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="352" x2="210" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="210" y1="249" x2="240" y2="249" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="310" x2="430" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="430" y1="352" x2="424" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="424" y1="344" x2="424" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="344" x2="416" y2="360" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="416" y1="352" x2="380" y2="352" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="380" y1="352" x2="380" y2="310" stroke="#8899bb" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="380" cy="310" r="2.6" fill="#8899bb"/><text x="420" y="336" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">CY</text><line x1="477" y1="20" x2="477" y2="60" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><line x1="477" y1="300" x2="477" y2="326" stroke="#00d4ff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><text x="477" y="14" fill="#00d4ff" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">ISOLATION</text><path d="M340,70 V185 H255 V200" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M397,255 V210 M397,197 V185 H360" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="8" stroke-opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:12px;margin:4px 0"><span style="display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;background:#f97316;margin:0 4px 0 10px"></span>주황=공급 경로</div><strong>기동 경로(주황, 상):</strong> HV+ 버스 → 기동 저항 Rst → VDD(VDD 커패시터를 UVLO 개시 임계값까지 충전, IC 스위칭 시작).<br><strong>정상 공급(주황, 하):</strong> 스위칭 확립 후 보조 권선 AUX → D2 정류 → VDD가 공급을 인계; AUX 전압은 권선비로 출력에 비례하며 1차측 레귤레이션(PSR)에서는 출력 전압 감지도 겸함.<br><strong>대기 전력:</strong> Rst는 고압 버스에 매달려 P≈V²/R이 상시 발생——365VDC에서 1MΩ이라도 0.13W를 소모, <30mW급 대기 규격을 직격. 대책: 저항값 증가(기동 시간 희생), 여러 개 직렬(내압), 또는 HV 기동 핀 내장(기동 후 차단되는 내장 JFET 전류원) 컨트롤러 선택.<div class="key-point">VDD 커패시터는 "기동부터 AUX 인계까지"의 공백을 버텨야 함——너무 작으면 딸꾹질(hiccup) 재기동. 면접 단골 추가 질문.</div>$vsq$);
